      <ul>
        <li><strong>No cash drain:</strong> Preserve year-start capital</li>
        <li><strong>Full investment:</strong> 100% of equipment cost</li>
        <li><strong>Working capital:</strong> Available for operations</li>
        <li><strong>Interest deduction:</strong> Additional tax benefit</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Equipment Planning for 2026</h2>

      <h3>Q1 Equipment (January-March)</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Buy early for maximum benefit</li>
        <li>Equipment for H1 projects</li>
        <li>Full year of tax deductions</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Q2 Equipment (April-June)</h3>

      <ul>
