      <ul>
        <li><strong>High taxable income expected?</strong> Buy equipment in January</li>
        <li><strong>Low taxable income expected?</strong> Spread purchases through year</li>
        <li><strong>Uncertain tax position?</strong> Start with small purchase, adjust later</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2026 Post-Year-End Action Plan</h2>

      <ol>
        <li><strong>Week 1 January:</strong> Review last year's results</li>
        <li><strong>Week 2 January:</strong> Plan this year's equipment needs</li>
        <li><strong>Week 3 January:</strong> Apply for January purchases</li>
        <li><strong>Week 4 January:</strong> Take delivery and start deductions</li>
        <li><strong>February-March:</strong> Continue Q1 equipment purchases</li>
        <li><strong>April onwards:</strong> Adjust strategy based on business</li>
      </ol>

